headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium
content:
Visit the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort to spin the Lucky Wheel. This week’s top prize is the Benefactor Schlagen GT, a sleek German roadster with personality and panache that’s slowly whirling on the podium nearby.

Discover the Lucky Wheel in The Diamond Casino & Resort lobby. If you win the top prize, your Podium Vehicle will be delivered to your selected Garage.
